title: BRICKELL STUNNER 50TH FLOOR OUTRAGEOUS VIEWS
posting_body: ['Large elegantly furnished penthouse with spectacular views of Biscayne Bay, Miami Beach, and the Miami skyline.', 'This corner residence features 3 Beds, 3.5 Baths, and 10’ ceilings with an open floor plan.', ' Kitchen complete with Calacatta marble, Italian finishes, Sub Zero, and Miele appliances.', ' Wood and marble flooring shine under the custom modern light fixtures found throughout.', ' The primary suite hosts dual walk-in closets, an oversized soaking jacuzzi tub & gorgeous water views.', 'Live the Epic lifestyle in the heart of Miami steps away from all of the hot spots with resort-style amenities including 2 restaurants, a fitness center, a lounge, a sauna + pool, and Zuma in your lobby.', ' Epic Residence is perfectly situated on the Miami River at Biscayne Bay, and gives over 200ft of water frontage for boat parking.', ' Pet friendly!', 'Call me', 'show contact info', 'for a showing!', ' Or hit reply above.', 'Christopher Smyk', 'Axis Realty Trust']
